EB64;\" rowspan=16| [[Bernard Hinault]]\n| style=\"background:#9CE97B;\" rowspan=16 | [[Sean Kelly (cyclist)|Sean Kelly]]\n| style=\"background:lightblue;\" | [[Sean Kelly (cyclist)|Sean Kelly]]\n| rowspan=16| {{ct|LVC|1985}}\n| ''no award''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 9|9]]\n| [[Maarten Ducrot]]\n| style=\"background:#FFA8A4;\" rowspan=15 | [[Luis Herrera (cyclist)|Luis Herrera]]\n| style=\"background:lightblue;\" rowspan=9 | [[Greg LeMond]]\n| [[Ren\u00e9 Bittinger]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 10|10]]\n| [[J\u00f8rgen V. Pedersen]]\n| [[Dominique Arnaud]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Prologue to Stage 11#Stage 11|11]]\n| [[Luis Herrera (cyclist)|Luis Herrera]]\n| [[Bernard Hinault]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 12|12]]\n| [[Fabio Parra]]\n| style=\"background:#FBCEB1;\" rowspan=12| [[Jozef Lieckens]]\n| [[Eduardo Chozas]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 13|13]]\n| [[Eric Vanderaerden]]\n| ''no award''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 14|14]]\n| [[Luis Herrera (cyclist)|Luis Herrera]]\n| [[Luis Herrera (cyclist)|Luis Herrera]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 15|15]]\n| [[Eduardo Chozas]]\n| [[Eduardo Chozas]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 16|16]]\n| [[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Vichot]]\n| [[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Vichot]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 17|17]]\n| [[Pedro Delgado]]\n| style=\"background:white;\" rowspan=7 | [[Fabio Parra]]\n| [[Pello Ruiz Cabestany]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de France, Stage 12 to Stage 22#Stage 18a|18a]]\n| [[Stephen Roche]]\n| style=\"background:lightblue;\" rowspan=4 | [[Sean Kelly (cyclist)|Sean Kelly]]\n| rowspan=2 | [[\u00c1lvaro Pino]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1985 Tour de F