erto Bressan]]|ITA}} || {{ct|BRD|1985}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | + 3h 45' 20\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 144\n| {{flagathlete|[[Manrico Ronchiato]]|ITA}} || {{ct|BRD|1985}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | + 4h 13' 48\"\n|}\n{{columns-start}}\n\n===Points classification===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Final points classification (1\u201310)<ref name=\"ld\">{{cite news|url=https://leiden.courant.nu/issue/LD/1985-07-22/edition/0/page/10|title=Tour in cijfers|date=22 July 1985|page=10|work=[[Leidsch Dagblad]]|via=Regionaal Archief Leiden|language=Dutch}}</ref><ref name=\"elmend\">{{cite news|url=http://hemeroteca.mundodeportivo.com/preview/1985/07/22/pagina-32/1121900/pdf.html|title=Clasificaciones oficiales|date=22 July 1985|accessdate=19 March 2012|language=Spanish|work=[[Mundo Deportivo]]}}</ref><ref name=\"het-parool-results\">{{cite news|title=Tour de France|url=https://resolver.kb.nl/resolve?urn=ABCDDD:010831141:mpeg21:p013|work=[[Het Parool]]|date=22 July 1985|page=14|language=Dutch|via=[[Delpher]]}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Rank\n! scope=\"col\" | Rider\n! scope=\"col\" | Team\n! scope=\"col\" | Points\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 1\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sean Kelly (cyclist)|Sean Kelly]]|IRE}} [[File:Jersey green.svg|20px|link=Points classification in the Tour de France|alt=A green jersey.]] || {{ct|SKIL|1985}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 434\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2\n| {{flagathlete|[[Greg LeMond]]|USA}} [[File:Jersey combined.svg|20px|link=Combination classification in the Tour de France|alt=A multi-coloured jersey.]] || {{ct|LVC|1985}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 332\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 3\n| {{flagathlete|[[Stephen Roche]]|IRE}} || {{ct|La Redoute|1985}} || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 279\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 4\n| {{flagathlete|[[Bernard Hinault]]|FRA}} [[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px|link=General classification in the Tour de France|alt=A yellow jersey.]] || {{ct|LVC|1985}}  || style=\"text-align:right;\" | 266\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 5\n| {{fla